ing period &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; First half of planning period</td><td>LGU, Concerned Agencies, DOH &nbsp; LGU, Concerned Agencies, DOH &nbsp; LGU, Concerned Agencies, DOH &nbsp; LGU, Concerned Agencies, DOH &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned Agencies, DOH, DENR</td></tr><tr><td>3. HousingousingHousing</td><td>To cut down the housing backlog through construction of affordable housing units and renovation of dilapidated units &nbsp; To help make subdivision housing available to more people &nbsp;</td><td>Poblacion, San Miguel &nbsp; Poblacion, San Miguel, Concerned barangays &nbsp;</td><td>First half of planning period &nbsp; Planning Period</td><td>LGU, Concerned agencies &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies</td></tr><tr><td>4. Social Welfare</td><td>To deliver basic services and improve social well-being of 60% of each of the different sectoral clienteles &nbsp; To establish a day care center in all the different barangays &nbsp; &nbsp; To improve the nutritional status &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; To decrease unemployment thru livelihood opportunities &nbsp;</td><td>Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide</td><td>First half of planning period &nbsp; Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; First three years of planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; First half of planning period</td><td>LGU, Concerned Agencies, DSWD &nbsp; LGU, Concerned Agencies, DSWD &nbsp; LGU, Concerned Agencies, DSWD, DOH &nbsp; LGU, Concerned Agencies, DSWD, DOLE</td></tr><tr><td>5. Protective Services</td><td>To increase the PNP and BFP manpower to meet existing minimum standards &nbsp; To provide support funds for the protective services sector &nbsp; &nbsp; To conduct regular and periodic training, community law enforcement, crime prevention, and calamity/disaster preparedness for Civilian Volunteer Organizations (CVOs) &nbsp; &nbsp; To involve the Disaster Coordinating Council, NGOs, barangay elders, and other concerned sectors in support of the PNP, BFP, and CVOs in the civic responsibility of community protection during periods of crisis &nbsp;</td><td>Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Poblacion &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide</td><td>First three years of planning period &nbsp; Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period</td><td>LGU, PNP &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, PNP &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned Agencies, PNP, DILG &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned Agencies, PNP, DILG &nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>6. Sports and Recreation</td><td>To upgrade all&nbsp; existing sports and recreational facilities by the end of the planning period &nbsp; To repackage open spaces and sports and recreation areas for tourism outdoor activities based on a tourism plan &nbsp;</td><td>Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide</td><td>Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period</td><td>LGU, Concerned Agencies &nbsp; LGU, Concerned Agencies</td></tr><tr><td>B. ECONOMIC</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>1. Agriculture</td><td>To increase the average yield of palay of in irrigated areas and rain-fed areas by 50% during the whole planning period &nbsp; To prepare a comprehensive agricultural master plan identifying the best suitable and profitable crops in all barangays, particularly in the barangays of Concordia, Sapa Grande and SapaPequena by the first year of the planning period &nbsp; To prepare a plan for livestock production and marketing in the first year of the planning period<em></em> &nbsp; &nbsp; To prepare a special plan for the management of pasturelands and open spaces, in connection with tourism plans, within the first year of the planning period<em></em> &nbsp; &nbsp; To declare unclassified forests as protected forests and prepare a forest management plan for the municipality within the first year of the planning period<em></em> &nbsp; To expand the coverage of the livestock breeding and dispersal program by the first three (3) years of the planning period. &nbsp; To increase poultry production by 100% in the whole planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; To rehabilitate more farm-to-market roads up to the year 2018 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; To construct and install facilities for communal irrigation systems in irrigated barangays and expand irrigable areas &nbsp; &nbsp; To provide enough multi-purpose drying pavements and construct farm post-harvest facilities within 3 years of the planning period <em>&nbsp;</em> &nbsp;</td><td>Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Concerned barangays &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp;</td><td>Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; First year of planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; First year of planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; First year of planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; First year of planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; First three years of planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2018 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Within three years of planning period</td><td>LGU, Concerned agencies, DA &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DA &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DA &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DA &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DA, DENR &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DA &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DA &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DA, DPWH &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DA, DPWH &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DA &nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>2. Commerce and Industry</td><td>To designate Poblacion and Pogoroac as commercial centers and prepare a special commercial plan for these areas<em></em> &nbsp; &nbsp; To designate Pogoruac and Papallasen as sites for industrial hubs<em></em> &nbsp; &nbsp; To fast track the putting up of infrastructure interventions related to commerce and trade<em></em> &nbsp; &nbsp; To construct stalls at selected barangay nexus points along the national highway in San Pascual, Papallasen, Don Matias and in Cacayasen<em></em> &nbsp; &nbsp; To establish ten small scale industries within the first half of the planning period<em></em> &nbsp; &nbsp; To use local government linkages to promote industry investments setting yearly targets &nbsp;</td><td>Poblacion, Pogoroac &nbsp; &nbsp; Poblacion, Pogoroac &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Concerned barangays &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Poblacion</td><td>First two years of planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; First two years of planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; First two years of planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; First two years of planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; First half of planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period</td><td>LGU, Concerned agencies, DTI &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DTI &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DTI &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DTI &nbsp; &nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>3. Tourism</td><td>To prioritize the development of the Caboangan beach area in Ilio-ilio for tourism activities Initiate the permanent designation&nbsp; of a tourism officer necessitating the creation of the appropriate plantilla item.<em></em> &nbsp; To draw up a tourism plan focused on beach and ecological-agricultural tourism &nbsp; To provide infrastructure support for tourism areas &nbsp; To market the specific brand of tourism in Burgos &nbsp; &nbsp; To set up an updated website for the municipality &nbsp; To provide an investment promotion plan for agri-tourism areas taking into account the agricultural sector plans. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</td><td>Ilio-ilio &nbsp; LGU &nbsp; &nbsp; Concerned barangays &nbsp; Concerned barangays Poblacion &nbsp; &nbsp; Poblacion &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide</td><td>First three years of planning period First Year of planning period &nbsp; First Year of planning period &nbsp; Planning period &nbsp; First half of planning period &nbsp; First year of planning period &nbsp; First year of planning period</td><td>LGU, Concerned agencies, DOT LGU &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DOT &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DOT LGU, Concerned agencies, DOT &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies &nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>C. INFRASTRUCTURE AND UTILITIES</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>1. Transportation</td><td>To be able to concrete or asphalt at least 80% of the remaining uncemented roads in the municipality within the planning period<em></em> &nbsp; To repair all barangay roads into an all-weather roads by the end of the planning period<em></em> &nbsp; To maintain or improve existing barangay bridges and foot bridges in the municipality. <em></em> &nbsp;</td><td>Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide</td><td>Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period</td><td>LGU, Concerned agencies, DPWH &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DPWH &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DPWH</td></tr><tr><td>2. Power</td><td>To provide domestic power connections to the remaining unserved households in the next five years. &nbsp; To upgrade and modernize power facilities by the end of the planning period. &nbsp;</td><td>Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide</td><td>Five years of planning period &nbsp; Planning period</td><td>LGU, Panelco 1 &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Panelco 1</td></tr><tr><td>3. Water</td><td>To establish Level III water supply of the Water District &nbsp; &nbsp; To install&nbsp; water treatment/chlorination equipment to the planned Level II water supply &nbsp; To put up determined number of new communal faucets &nbsp;</td><td>Concerned barangays &nbsp; Ilio-ilio &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide</td><td>Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; First two years of planning period &nbsp; First two years of planning period</td><td>LGU, Concerned agencies, DOST &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DOST &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies</td></tr><tr><td>4. Communication</td><td>To upgrade and modernize the equipment of the Post Office and the Telecommunications &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; To improve the coverage of other communication facilities especially the cellular phone &nbsp;</td><td>Poblacion &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide</td><td>Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period</td><td>LGU, Telecommunication groups &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Telecommunication groups</td></tr><tr><td>5.Environmental Protection and Disaster Risk Reduction</td><td>To prepare an environmental protection plan providing a plan unifying the individual plans of the different sectors in this area &nbsp; To prepare the Disaster Risk Reduction Plan for the whole Municipality &nbsp; Structure educational component</td><td>Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Muncipality-wide</td><td>1<sup>st</sup>-2<sup>nd</sup> years of the planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; 1<sup>st</sup> year of the planning period &nbsp; Planning period</td><td>LGU &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->', 'PRIORITY PROGRAMS AND PROJECTS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'priority-programs-and-projects', '', '', '2020-09-13 10:05:51', '2020-09-13 10:05:51', '', 98, 'https://192.168.1.5/git/burgos-website/?page_id=116', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(117, 2, '2020-09-13 09:59:08', '2020-09-13 09:59:08', '<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>SECTOR</td><td>PROPOSED PROGRAMS/ PROJECTS</td><td>LOCATION</td><td>YEAR OF IMPLEMENTATION</td><td>IMPLEMENTING AGENCY</td></tr><tr><td>A. SOCIAL SERVICES</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>1. Education</td><td>To rehabilitate all the&nbsp; school buildings in need of repair by the end of the planning period &nbsp; To provide centralized elementary schools with modern teaching equipment. &nbsp; To allocate funds for the training of school teachers and other school personnel &nbsp; To convert selected and appropriate buildings to much needed facilities as laboratories and clinics for all schools &nbsp; To establish libraries or reading centers in schools without the facility &nbsp;</td><td>Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Poblacion &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide</td><td>Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning Period &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period</td><td>LGU, Concerned agencies, DepEd &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DepEd &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DepEd &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DepEd &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DepEd</td></tr><tr><td>2. Health</td><td>To reduce morbidity and mortality rates of infectious diseases. &nbsp; To decrease the number of malnourished children by 100% &nbsp; &nbsp; To provide&nbsp; barangay health centers in all barangays &nbsp; &nbsp; To upgrade existing health centers in terms of personnel, medicines and equipment &nbsp; &nbsp; To develop the municipal dumpsite including its access road, facilities &nbsp; &nbsp;</td><td>Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; San Miguel</td><td>Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; Plann