orination equipment to the planned Level II water supply &nbsp; To put up determined number of new communal faucets &nbsp;</td><td>Concerned barangays &nbsp; Ilio-ilio &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide</td><td>Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; First two years of planning period &nbsp; First two years of planning period</td><td>LGU, Concerned agencies, DOST &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies, DOST &nbsp; LGU, Concerned agencies</td></tr><tr><td>4. Communication</td><td>To upgrade and modernize the equipment of the Post Office and the Telecommunications &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; To improve the coverage of other communication facilities especially the cellular phone &nbsp;</td><td>Poblacion &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide</td><td>Planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Planning period</td><td>LGU, Telecommunication groups &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU, Telecommunication groups</td></tr><tr><td>5.Environmental Protection and Disaster Risk Reduction</td><td>To prepare an environmental protection plan providing a plan unifying the individual plans of the different sectors in this area &nbsp; To prepare the Disaster Risk Reduction Plan for the whole Municipality &nbsp; Structure educational component</td><td>Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Municipality-wide &nbsp; &nbsp; Muncipality-wide</td><td>1<sup>st</sup>-2<sup>nd</sup> years of the planning period &nbsp; &nbsp; 1<sup>st</sup> year of the planning period &nbsp; Planning period</td><td>LGU &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU &nbsp; &nbsp; LGU</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->', 'PRIORITY PROGRAMS AND PROJECTS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '116-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-09-13 10:10:32', '2020-09-13 10:10:32', '', 116, 'https://192.168.1.5/git/burgos-website/?p=120', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
